Package: passwd-messagebus
Version: 20230717
Revision: 1
Description: User/group for the dbus daemon
Type: nosource
License: Public Domain
Maintainer: Fink Core Group <fink-core@lists.sourceforge.net>
Depends: passwd-core (>= 20230717-1)
CompileScript: <<
	### Get the docfiles from passwd-core
	cp -p %p/share/doc/passwd-core/README* .
<<
InstallScript: /usr/bin/true
DocFiles: README.md README.removing-users.md
PostInstScript: <<
	### <script> -n 'username' -i 'Real Name' -h 'home' -s 'shell' -g 'groupname' -m 'Group membership string'
	%p/sbin/update-passwd -n 'messagebus' -i 'messagebus (dbus) daemon,,,' -h '%p/var/run/dbus' -g 'messagebus' -m 'messagebus'
<<
DescDetail: <<
This package adds administrative user and group entries for the
package "dbus" to your user database. These are needed to
protect the data used by this package.
<<
